Checked out trousers

 - run
     cvs -d:pserver:anonymous@trousers.cvs.sourceforge.net:/cvsroot/trousers login
   to login into cvs server, type Enter directly for password;
 - run
     cvs -z3 -d:pserver:anonymous@trousers.cvs.sourceforge.net:/cvsroot/trousers co -P trousers
   to check out trousers module;
 - run
     cvs -z3 -d:pserver:anonymous@trousers.cvs.sourceforge.net:/cvsroot/trousers co -P testsuite
   to check out testsuite module;
 - refer to "Linux_LCP_Tools_User_Manual.pdf" to build trousers.

Go to http://sourceforge.net/projects/trousers/ for more information about trousers.
